Box Hunter  
==========  
Try to get the black box without breaking it.  
  
If you don't have Linux or you don't want to install anything,  
try the WebGL version: [Play Box Hunter Online](http://eternalvoid.net/code/box-hunter-online)  

Controls  
--------  
Left and Right:  Left and Right Arrows  
Jump:  Left Ctrl  
Restart Current Level:  F1  
Exit:  Esc  
